Within which directory will you find configuration files for the Postfix mail server on aDebian-based Linux server?
A)  /etc/postfixd
B)  /var/postfix
C)  /etc/postfix
D)  /var/postfixd
C
C. The configuration files for Postfix are stored in /etc/postfix on a Debian server.Of the other answers, none of the directories exist by default.
